@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tigppu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(v0) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.23 * v0 + 0.26)))
    v0 = 0.59
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.75 / v1 + 0.01) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.83)))
    v0 = 0.96
    data[tid] = v0
